00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:30.000
 Please go to the phone settings &gt; Wireless &amp; Internet: Status column to pull down and click "Settings" 

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:40.000
 Click on the mobile network and enable it. Then select the network sharing and portable wireless base station. 

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:50.000
 Network sharing and portable wireless base station selection to "USB network sharing" Network mode selects priority network mode to "WCDMA only" 

00:00:52.000 --> 00:01:00.000
 Mobile phone and computer connected by USB cable 

00:01:02.000 --> 00:01:10.000
 Computer &gt; BenQ A3 CD player disk slot 

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:20.000
 Mobile phone USB computer connection, re-select "USB storage device" 

00:01:22.000 --> 00:01:30.000
 Computer installation "BenQ_A3_USBDRIVER_V1_001.EXE Next step (Next &gt; ) 

00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:40.000
 Press Install to install 

00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:50.000
 The system automatically pops up the "device driver installation wizard, please click the step to install the warning window message, please press to continue installation 

00:01:52.000 --> 00:02:00.000
 After the installation is successful, please click "Finish" to find "Found New Hardware (BenQ A3 Rndis)" in the lower right corner of the desktop. 

00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:10.000
 “Find new hardware wizard” appears, please select “Automatic installation software” and click Next. 

00:02:12.000 --> 00:02:20.000
 The installation warning window message appears, please press to continue installation 

00:02:22.000 --> 00:02:30.000
 After the installation is successful, please press "Finish". In the lower right corner of the desktop, "Found a message that the new hardware is available" will appear. Your new hardware is installed and ready to use." 

00:02:32.000 --> 00:02:40.000
 Go to my computer and press the right button &gt; Administration &gt; Device Manager &gt; Network Interface Card to confirm that the network interface card has been added with BenQ A3 Rndis and the status is connected. 

00:02:42.000 --> 00:02:50.000
 Console &gt; Network and Sharing Center, there will be a new area connection (ex. area connection 4), confirm that the connection is ready to use 

